snippet.title: PunBall - ANNIVERSARY PARTY!
snippet.description:
It's our anniversary party! Don't be shy, one tap's all it takes!

-Brand New Gameplay: Apollo's Ruins Exploration
-Brand New System: Artifacts
-Newly Added Chapters: 141-160
-Trial Tower floors increased to 200
-PunPass Season 7: PunBall 1-Year Anniversary Party
-All-new anniversary events available all month long!

Download now for free:
iOS: https://apps.apple.com/app/punball/id1585781366
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.habby.punball
